---
title: Beef Brisket & Red Wine Jus Filo Pie with Pear & Almond Salad
description: The classic beef pie is getting a serious upgrade tonight, enough to pull out the fancy plates when you serve up. Beef brisket is wrapped in a blanket of golden filo, with a tomato and red wine jus sauce soaking in as it bakes. Even the pear salad gets a nutty finish with almonds sprinkled on top. We think this is a five star pie for sure.
